snippet.title: Bucks Busters (Multiplayer Online Game)
snippet.description:
Bucks Busters is a multiplayer online game with social mechanics. It's an economic strategy game that engages you into the comic narrative of the office life.

Build dirty tricks, generate ideas, protect them or steal others. And the strongest will win, because only a great strategist and diplomat can survive in this office war! Here, you are the head of the office and you have 5 employees at your disposal. There are 3 more offices like yours. The goal is to defeat competitors by all available means in order to become the best office.

Play now in your browser: https://bucksbusters.com
